{"tid":953003,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲打想學琴？","createTime":"2018-12-23T15:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T03:43:05.000Z","uid":190369,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2d32534a5571fb1945e8de9006d1ee19eb784917","tid":953003,"uid":190369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"上個Post之後收到唔少查詢及試堂，感謝各位巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有見及此，我再重新開個新Post，希望幫到各位。有問題或想了解更多，可以隨時Telegram聯絡我。<br />\n<br />\n單對單上堂比小組上堂好？<br />\n唔一定，兩種模式各有好處。香港學習樂器普遍單對單授課，但小組型式上堂可以學習同其他人合奏既技巧、唔同崗位要注意既事項等，甚至同其他人合奏係學習音樂中非常重要既一環！<br />\n<br />\n要有音樂認識先可以上小組堂？<br />\n唔一定！我會將程度相約既學員擺係同一個小組上堂，所以唔洗怕跟唔上進度，甚至一段時間後可以再重新編排，盡量令每位都可以跟得上進度，而且又學到野<br />\n<br />\n學習Jazz/Pop前要先學古典音樂？<br />\n唔一定。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打可以係呢到或Telegram聯絡我了解更多<br />\n[url]Telegram : <a href=\"https://t.me/Bi_FL[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBi_FL%5B%2Furl%5D&d=TnS4iv0AzTN1VcoBQxMwhDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5f8ad09d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Bi_FL[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n第一堂免費！甚至可以純粹上黎我教室了解下，之後再決定學唔學都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都歡迎各位係呢個Post交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f083ae4b2fe39da15e5f984474f06615f57b9cdb","tid":953003,"uid":190369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bc4407d98569b5f70dbd6b1e2785714ee26589","tid":953003,"uid":190369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3547e0f76230840d861c4e6852fca2e9a62747e","tid":953003,"uid":190369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid